d":83194,"like":244,"dislike":5,"score":239,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"咁多位早晨，我今日嚟，係想同你哋講個故事嘅：<br />\n<br />\n喺幾年前<br />\n我同一個寡婦結咗婚<br />\n佢有一個已成年嘅女<br />\n後來嫁咗比我老豆<br />\n<br />\n咁我繼女就做咗我後媽<br />\n而我老豆就做咗我女婿<br />\n<br />\n兩年後我老婆同我生咗一個仔<br />\n佢喺我後媽嘅同母異父嘅細佬<br />\n我個仔叫我「老豆」<br />\n我就叫我個仔「舅父」<br />\n<br />\n我繼女又為我老豆生咗一個仔<br />\n佢喺我細佬<br />\n但佢又要叫我外公<br />\n<br />\n我喺我老婆個老公<br />\n但喺我老婆喺我後媽個阿媽喎<br />\n所以我喺自己嘅外公<br />\n<br />\n到咗新年<br />\n嚟料喇<br />\n<br />\n我就同我後媽同我老豆<br />\n即係同我繼女同女婿交換利是<br />\n<br />\n我封廿蚊比我個仔<br />\n佢話：「多謝老豆！」<br />\n我又答返佢：「唔洗，舅父！喺呢，咁我嗰封呢？」<br />\n「你都痴線，我結咗婚喇咩？」唉，我自己都亂咗... <br />\n<br />\n食團年飯嗰陣<br />\n我喺抬面上面放咗一封一千蚊利是<br />\n再拎返封利是上手<br />\n叫咗聲：「多謝外公！」"},{"pid":"bc1370aaa48a1fdc26ae76b85fae991d8e4b2cd7","tid":773394,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"08d3410f92e8a430a0d006bc2bb3916e0fed5bd8","tid":773394,"uid":169340,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1741da00531bcfee8b4c69e0fc50705365b4cef8","tid":773394,"uid":3775,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"78ed5004b4f5447f21f0935285e98bd170ae1a84","tid":773394,"uid":161865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"有冇bio人講下捐丸啲精子係應該define做邊個嘅精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.theverge.com/platform/amp/2018/4/26/17286728/penis-scrotum-transplant-surgery-us-veteran-johns-hopkins-testicles-ethics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fplatform%2Famp%2F2018%2F4%2F26%2F17286728%2Fpenis-scrotum-transplant-surgery-us-veteran-johns-hopkins-testicles-ethics&d=1pE96L4oep1cJqjzI4q3NMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2e557533\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.theverge.com/platform/amp/2018/4/26/17286728/penis-scrotum-transplant-surgery-us-veteran-johns-hopkins-testicles-ethics</a